{"prompt": "Generate a website for a community non-profit. The website should be elegant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Connect</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2a628f; /* Elegant Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #618ca8; /* Lighter shade of blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            --footer-bg: #1f4966;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .content-section {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .content-section h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .content-section p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-bg);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Community Connect</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#mission\">Our Mission</a>\n        <a href=\"#programs\">Programs</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero-section\">\n            <h2>Building a Stronger Tomorrow, Together</h2>\n            <p>Empowering our community through connection, support, and shared initiatives. Discover how you can make a difference.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Involved</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>About Us</h3>\n            <p>Community Connect is a non-profit organization dedicated to fostering a vibrant and supportive environment for all members of our community. We believe in the power of collective action to address local needs and create positive change. Founded on principles of collaboration and compassion, we strive to be a beacon of hope and a catalyst for progress.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"mission\" class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>Our Mission</h3>\n            <p>Our mission is to empower individuals and strengthen community bonds by providing essential resources, educational opportunities, and a platform for meaningful engagement. We aim to create a space where everyone feels valued, supported, and inspired to contribute to the well-being of our shared home.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"programs\" class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>Our Programs</h3>\n            <p>We offer a range of programs designed to meet diverse community needs. From youth mentorship and educational workshops to senior support services and local environmental initiatives, there's a way for everyone to connect and contribute. Explore our initiatives and find where you fit in.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">View Our Work</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>Connect With Us</h3>\n            <p>Have questions, ideas, or want to volunteer? We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us through any of the channels below.</p>\n            <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@communityconnect.org</p>\n            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Community Lane, Our Town, ST 12345</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@communityconnect.org\" class=\"cta-button\">Send a Message</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Community Connect. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}